23464 Urs Felber interview at Neocon on Vimeo] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20110714162901/http://www.neoconeast.com/tasks/sites/NeoconEast/assets/File/061908_002.pdf Urs Felber, Neoconeast] * [http://www.lifestylesmagazine.com/website/archive/216.html Urs Felber, Lifestyle magazine] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20120225084207/http://www.interiordesign.net/article/480142-Swiss_Furniture_Manufacturer_to_Open_25_U_S_Showrooms.php Dietiker and Urs Felber, Interior Design magazine] * [http://www.larevuedudesign.com/2010/07/07/selection-design-suisse-3/ Hommage a Urs Felber, La Revue du Design] *[http://www.insideoutcontracts.com/ Insideout Contracts – Contract Furniture specialists]
